Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:07.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain　消した記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:13.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely　物語の常が今見せる言葉で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:18.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}どうしたって　変えられない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}目的を忘れないでいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:29.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}誰が決めたんだ　そんな生き方らしくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:35.32,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}やりたいこと貫く力　それこそが強さだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}分かっているから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.91,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:48.58,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}歩んできた日々を　懐かしむ意味を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:57.38,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}諦めることはない　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:06.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}心の光を　覚えてるうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:15.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.79,0:01:07.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Refrain 抹去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.25,0:01:13.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Rely 故事总在只言片语间展开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:15.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Don't end this, won't change it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:18.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}无论怎么做都无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}但不要忘记你的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:29.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}别人定义出的你 不是真实的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:35.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}坚持自我的力量 才是真的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}这就是我的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:41.91,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:48.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我会回忆走过的路 找出价值所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.67,0:01:50.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:57.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我会坚持到最后 不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:06.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}趁你心里还亮着一团光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:10.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:15.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
